ght: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Đối tượng sử dụng:\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;- Dùng cho người bị thiểu năng tuần hoàn máu não: chóng mặt, ù tai, hoa mắt, giảm trí nhớ, di chứng do tai biến mạch máu não;\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;- Người cao tuổi, người làm việc trí óc nhiều, hay bị căng thẳng, mệt mỏi; cần tăng khả năng tập trung và trí nhớ.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Cách dùng:\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Sử dụng 1 ống mỗi ngày. Nên pha loãng với nửa ly nước.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.25in;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Lắc ống trước khi pha loãng.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.25in;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;img src=&quot;http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-VWW33srGkY4/UigFwjLppHI/AAAAAAAAAdQ/jRZD5OBRs-Y/s320/TRALY+BRAIN.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; align=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0px&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.25in;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;Với hàm lượng Ginkgo Biloba cao kết hợp với các dược liệu khác như nhân sâm, lá xô thơm việt quất vừa có tác dụng bồi bổ cơ thể vừa hỗ trợ tăng tác dụng của sản phẩm.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-indent: 0.25in;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 18.399999618530273px; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;Chi tiết xin tham khảo tại:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/an-than-tang-cuong-th-nao/traly-brain&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/an-than-tang-cuong-th-nao/traly-brain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '175000', '', NULL, '2014-02-11 00:00:00', 'TRALY BRAIN.jpg', 0, 722, 1, 0),
(55, 2, 0, 1, 0, 25, 31, 0, 'TRALY SAMIN - Sự lựa chọn tối ưu trong điều trị về khớp', '\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;TRALY SAMIN&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;là sản phẩm của công ty TNHH TM Dược phẩm Trang Ly&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;với hàm lượng glucosamin 500mg và bào chế dạng ống uống&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;nên người sử dụng có thể hoàn toàn yên tâm&lt;/span&gt;', '\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;TRALY SAMIN&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;là sản phẩm của công ty TNHH TM Dược phẩm Trang Ly&amp;nbsp;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;với hàm lượng glucosamin 500mg và bào chế dạng ống uống&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;nên người sử dụng có thể hoàn toàn yên tâm .&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;1. Tại sao sử dụng Glusosamine trong VIÊM KHỚP?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Điều trị tận gốc, cải thiện tổn thương khớp (MRI).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Glucosamin thúc đẩy sự tái tạo phần mềm quanh khớp.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Glucosamin không chỉ có tác dụng giảm viêm, giảm đau mà còn ngăn chặn bệnh tiến triển điểm này thuốc kháng viêm không có.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;2. Tại sao nói Glucosamine điều trị tận gốc bệnh viêm khớp?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Bởi vì glucosamin kích thích tế bào sụn khớp tăng tổng hợp và tăng sản xuất chất nhầy dịch khớp nên tăng độ nhớt, khả năng bôi trơn của dịch khớp.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ức chế các enzym phá hủy sụn khớp như collagenase, phospholipase A2 và giảm các gốc tự do superoxid phá hủy các tế bào sụn.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Tăng tổng hợp Collagen và có tác dụng kháng viêm.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot; _mce_href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;3. Sử dụng bao lâu thì bắt đầu có kết quả?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Trường hợp thông thường: Dạng lỏng sau 2 tuần.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Trường hợp nặng: Dạng lỏng sau 1 tháng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;4. Tại sao dùng Glucosamine dạng lỏng tốt hơn dạng viên?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dạng viên: Viên thuốc giải phóng chậm hơn, hấp thu kém hơn so với dạng lỏng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dạng lỏng: Hấp thu nhanh, đến khớp với nồng độ cao, dễ dung nạp, được ưa chuộng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;5. Dùng trong bao lâu?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dùng điều trị cho đến khi hết các triệu chứng khớp.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dùng lâu dài để bồi bổ sụn khớp và ngăn tái phát.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot; _mce_href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;6. Tác dụng phụ của thuốc là gì?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Cho thấy ưu điểm của Glucosamine: rất hiếm tác dụng phụ như thuốc kháng viêm như:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;üLoét, thủng dạ dày.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;üXuất huyết dưới da, mũi, dạ dày, khớp, não.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;üDị ứng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;7\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;. Nếu dùng Glucosamine thấy khó chịu ở dạ dày thì làm thế nào?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Một số rất hiếm người sử dụng có thể thấy khó chịu ở vùng dạ dày&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Pha với nhiều nước hơn (1,5 - 2L)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Ngưng thuốc kháng viêm&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Hoặc pha loãng ít và uống ngay trước hoặc trong bữa ăn.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Glucosamine không có hại cho dạ dày. ngược lại còn giúp tạo chất nhờn che chở dạ dày và tạo collagen giúp vết loét dạ dày mau lành.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot; _mce_href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;8. Người dị ứng với hải sản có dùng được Glucosamine không?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Vẫn dùng được trên thực tế.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Mặc dù về lý thuyết nhà sản xuất cẩn thận lưu ý.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Nguyên nhân gây dị ứng là thịt hải sản, không nằm trong vỏ hải sản.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;9. Loại Glucosamine nào tốt nhất?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Glucosamine hydrochloride.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Dạng lỏng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Tube tiện dụng.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p style=&quot;font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;&quot;&gt;Chi tiết xin xem tại:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot; _mce_href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br /&gt;\r\n &lt;/div&gt;', '180000', '', NULL, '2014-02-12 00:00:00', 'Traly Samin.jpg', 0, 712, 1, 0);
