(62, 2, 0, 1, 0, 25, 31, 0, 'Traly Brest – Để hoàn hảo hơn trong mắt phái mạnh', '\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Sản phẩm Traly Brest với 16 thành phần&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 24px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 48px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;không chỉ có tác dụng tuyệt vời đối với những phụ nữ có vòng 1 nhỏ gây thiếu tự tin mà còn giúp cho những phụ nữ sau sinh lấy lại được vóc dáng săn chắc và căng tròn cho bộ ngực không bị chảy sệ&lt;/span&gt;', '\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Sản phẩm\r\nTraly Brest với 16 thành phần&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; không chỉ có tác dụng tuyệt vời\r\nđối với những phụ nữ có vòng 1 nhỏ gây thiếu tự tin mà còn giúp cho những phụ\r\nnữ sau sinh lấy lại được vóc dáng săn chắc và căng tròn cho bộ ngực không bị\r\nchảy sệ.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&lt;/a&gt;\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Giúp nuôi dưỡng bầu ngực, đồng thời kích\r\nthích các tuyến, các tế bào mô ngực phát triển, gia tăng tính đàn hồi của các\r\nmô liên kết giúp ngực săn chắc.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Bổ sung các dưỡng chất cân thiết cho cơ thể.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Giúp cho tóc, da mịn màng.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Vì công thức sản phẩm được cải tiến có tác dụng\r\nnhanh chóng hỗ trợ, bổ sung \r\n   &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;estrogen&lt;/span&gt;\r\ntự nhiên thúc đẩy sự phát triển của các mô ngực mới, giúp ngực săn chắc và nở\r\nto tự nhiên mà không hề có tác dụng phụ.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:1.0in;mso-add-space: auto;text-align:justify;line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;16 thành phần có trong sản phẩm\r\nTraly Brest: \r\n     &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpLast&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Pueraria Mirifica: &lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Mang\r\nnhững hoạt tính estrogen cao nhất trong số các estrogen thực vật do có cấu trúc\r\ntương tự như estradiol, là loại estrogen có thể tìm thấy ở những phụ nữ đang\r\ntrong thời kỳ cho con bú đặc biệt có tuyến vú rất phát triển, giúp kích thích\r\ncác tuyến ngực, mô ngực, giúp cho bầu ngực phát triển và cơ ngực đều đặn hơn.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;text-align:justify;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-style: italic;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglyb.blogspot.com/2014/02/traly-brest-e-hoan-hao-hon-trong-mat.html&quot;&gt;http://tranglyb.blogspot.com/2014/02/traly-brest-e-hoan-hao-hon-trong-mat.html&lt;/a&gt;\r\n     &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Tinh chất mầm yến mạch:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Giàu\r\nchất xơ dinh dưỡng giúp loại bỏ độc tố ra khỏi cơ thể làm cho da mượt mà và\r\ntrắng sáng. Giúp điều tiết lưu lượng máu, giảm lượng cholesterol và lượng mỡ dư\r\nthừa trong má.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Tinh chất mầm đậu nành:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;\r\nGenistein và isoflavon có trong mầm đậu nành giống như kích tố giới tính nữ\r\nchính là oestrogen, là một loại kích tố giới tính nữ đóng một vai trò vô cùng\r\nquan trọng trong việc điều chỉnh sức khỏe sinh sản, kinh nguyệt:\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Vai trò của kích tố giới tính nữ - Oestrogen:\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Làm tăng độ dày của mô mỡ ở ngực, mông. Tác động\r\nlên sự tăng trưởng và kích thước của bầu ngực, giúp ngực đầy đặn.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Có tác dụng ức chế sự phát triển của các nang\r\nlông, mang đến cho nữ giới làn da mềm mại, chân lông nhỏ, thông thoáng.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Tác động tới hệ xương giúp bạn gái có vai hẹp, eo\r\nthon, có xương chậu rộng, hình thành nên dáng vẻ đường nét mềm mại.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Tác động tới hệ thần kinh và giúp nữ giới có tích\r\ncách trầm tĩnh, dịu dàng.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Semen Pruni Armeniacae (Dầu hạnh nhân): &lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Chứa\r\nnhiều vitamin E giúp cho tóc mềm mại sáng bón, phòng chống và hỗ trợ trong việc\r\nngăn ngừa mụn đầu đen, mụn nhọt, giúp làn da mịn màng và chống lão hóa cho da.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Sữa ong chúa:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Có tác\r\ndụng dược lý như thúc đẩy việc tổng hợp nội tiết tố, thúc đẩy quá trình sinh\r\ntrưởng, dậy thì khả năng sinh sản của cơ thể. Giúp kháng khuẩn, chống viêm,\r\nnâng cao sức đề kháng và miễn dịch của cơ thể\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&lt;/a&gt;\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Betacaroten:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Nhóm\r\nchất beta carotene là sắc tố tự nhiên trong rau quả, khi vào cơ thể beta\r\ncaroten chuyển hóa thành vitamin A. Đây là chất quan trọng trong việc tăng\r\ncường hệ miễn dịch, nuôi dưỡng làn da và ổn định đường tiêu hóa, thúc đẩy tế\r\nbào tăng trưởng khỏe mạnh.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Acid patonthetic:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Tạo\r\nđiều kiện thuận lợi cho quá trình phát triển và độ bền vững của da cũng như\r\nniêm mạc. Hoạt động chính đó là phan giải lượng dầu thừa trên da - nguyên nhân\r\ntrực tiếp của sự hình thành mụn trứng cá và làm se các lỗ chân lông.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Pyridoxin:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Có tác động trong sự\r\nchuyển hóa protein, kích thích hệ thần kinh, tăng cường hệ miễn dịch, tham gia\r\nvào quá trình tổng hợp hormon và tế bào hồng cầu. Thiếu hụt có thể dẫn đến\r\nthiếu máu nguyên bào sắt, viêm da tăng bã nhờn, khô nứt môi, rụng tóc.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Cyanocobalamin:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Giúp\r\nduy trì tình trạng khỏe mạnh của tế bào thần kinh và hồng cầu. Ngoài ra còn\r\ntham gia vào quá trình chuyển hóa lipid, giúp da săn chắc.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Selen:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Tác dụng chống oxy hóa, chống\r\nlại sự lão hóa trong cơ thể, tăng cường khả năng miễn dịch cho cơ thể.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Vitamin D:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Giúp cho xương và hệ\r\nmiễn dịch trong cơ thể hoạt động tốt. Vitamin D còn tham gia một số chức năng\r\nbài tiết, phát triển hệ sinh sản và da ở nữ giới.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Sắt&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;: Sắt đóng vai trò rất quan\r\ntrọng trong quá trình vận chuyển các chất dinh dưỡng trong cơ thể tạo nên những\r\nthay đổi trên cơ thể cũng như sinh lý của bạn gái tuổi dậy thì. Thiếu sắt da dẻ\r\nxanh xao, môi khô.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Kẽm:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Kẽm can thiệp vào nhiều chuyển\r\nhóa, chuyển hóa glucid, protein, và acid nucleic. Kem còn là yếu tố quan trọng\r\nthúc đẩy sự tiết kích thích tố, làm tăng sự phát triển của vòng ngực.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Canxi:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Là thành phần không thể thiếu\r\nvới sự phát triển xương, răng, sự đông máu, hoạt động truyền tín hiệu của tế\r\nbào thần kinh, đạc biệt là trong giai đoạn dậy thì.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; line-height: 150%; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;-&amp;nbsp; Crom:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt; line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt; Là nguyên tố vi lượng tác động\r\nđến sự chuyển hóa của chất béo bằng việc đốt cháy lipid, giảm lượng cholesterol\r\ncó hại trong cơ thể. Crom còn là chất thúc đẩy sự hấp thụ glucose và làm cho\r\nmông, ngực căng tròn, săn chắc.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpLast&quot; style=&quot;text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in; line-height:150%;tab-stops:0in&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%; mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Khi sử dụng bạn chỉ cần pha 1 gói với 150ml nước\r\nấm, ngày 2 lần. Các chị em phụ nữ có thể thoải mái làm việc và vui chơi mà\r\nkhông phải mất nhiều thời gian tìm tòi hỏi han các biện pháp rồi lại mất thời\r\ngian tiếp để lựa chọn, chế biến.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;Để biết\r\nchi tiết hơn bạn có thể truy cập website:\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-left:.5in;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;mso-bidi-font-family:Calibri&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/san-pham-lam-dep/traly-brest-tang-kich-thuoc-vong-1&lt;/a&gt;\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', NULL, '2014-02-19 00:00:00', 'Traly Brest 2.jpg', 0, 697, 1, 0),
(63, 2, 0, 1, 0, 25, 31, 0, 'Đẩy lùi bệnh gan với Traly Arginin', '\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;Việc kết hợp&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglyb.blogspot.com/2013/12/traly-arginin-su-ket-hop-hoan-hao-cua.html&quot;&gt;Arginin&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;và&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;diệp hạ châu&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;trong&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/tieu-hoa-gan-mat/traly-arginin&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 24px;&quot;&gt;Traly Arginin&lt;/a&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 24px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;sẽ tạo ra tác dụng hiệp đồng, làm tăng tác dụng bảo vệ tế bào gan, tăng cường chức năng gan và làm giảm các triệu chứng của bệnh gan.&lt;/span&gt;', '\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;Ở Việt Nam cũng như nhiều quốc gia đang\r\nphát triển khác, tỷ lệ người mắc &lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglya.blogspot.com/2014/02/lua-chon-san-pham-ieu-tri-benh-ve-gan.html&quot;&gt;bệnh\r\nviêm gan&lt;/a&gt; và ung thư gan rất cao. Theo một số tài liệu thống kê, nước ta có\r\nkhoảng 20% dân số có các bệnh liên quan tới gan như các bệnh viêm gan, xơ gan,\r\nviêm gan virus, &lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglypharma.com/tin-moi/gan-nhiem-mo-can-benh-thuong-gap&quot;&gt;gan\r\nnhiễm mỡ&lt;/a&gt; và đặc biệt là ung thư gan – một trong những nguyên nhân gây ra tử\r\nvong cao nhất ở Việt Nam.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://tranglya.blogspot.com/2014/02/cac-loai-thao-duoc-lam-mat-gan-giai-oc.html&quot;&gt;Gan&lt;/a&gt;\r\nlà cơ quan đảm nhận rất nhiều vai trò quan trọng trong cơ thể như: \r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%; mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;!--\r\n [if !supportLists]\r\n  --&gt;\r\n  -\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [endif]\r\n --&gt;\r\n  \r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;Chuyển hóa:\r\nglucid, lipid, protid từ dạng đơn thành dạng phức hợp dữ trữ khi cơ thể thừa,\r\nvà ngược lại dị hóa các phức hợp để tạo năng lượng cung cấp khi cơ thể thiếu.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%; mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [if !supportLists]\r\n  --&gt;\r\n  -\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [endif]\r\n --&gt;\r\n  \r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;Giúp đông máu\r\nvà chống đông máu: gan dự trữ và sản xuất ra các yếu tố tham gia vào quá trình\r\nđông máu, do đó khi bị suy gan thường có biểu hiện rối loạn đông máu. Gan cũng\r\ntạo ra một lượng lớn chất có tác dụng chống đông máu là heparin.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%; mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [if !supportLists]\r\n  --&gt;\r\n  -\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [endif]\r\n --&gt;\r\n  \r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;Giải độc và bài\r\ntiết các chất độc ra khỏi cơ thể: lá gan đóng một vai trò chính yếu trong việc\r\nloại bỏ ra khỏi máu các sản phẩm độc hại sinh ra từ ruột hay nội sinh (do cơ thể\r\ntạo ra), các thuốc sử dụng, ure. Gan chuyển đổi chúng thành những chất mà cơ thể\r\ncó thể loại bỏ dễ dàng.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%; mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [if !supportLists]\r\n  --&gt;\r\n  -\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [endif]\r\n --&gt;\r\n  \r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;background-color: white; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial;&quot;&gt;Tạo máu và dự\r\ntrữ máu: gan với hệ thống xoang mạch rộng lớn có thể chứa được tới 2 lit máu và\r\nsẽ đi vào tuần hoàn khi cần thiết.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle&quot; style=&quot;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:150%; mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;!--\r\n [if !suppo