(68, 1, 18, 1, 0, 14, 6, 0, 'Gạo Vigigaba, nhà phân phối gạo vigigaba, đại lý gạo Vigigaba, cung cấp, thông tin, giá cả mua bán gạo vi', '\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt; margin-left:0in;mso-line-height-alt:12.0pt&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;Gạo Vigigaba&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt; margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:12.0pt&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;-\r\nGạo mầm Vibigaba&amp;nbsp;là loại gạo lứt được lên men trong điều kiện thích hợp để\r\ncác enzyme trong hạt gạo được kích hoạt tạo nhiều&amp;nbsp;chất dinh dưỡng.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt; margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:12.0pt&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;-\r\nTrong đó đáng lưu ý là hàm lượng chất GABA (Gamma aminobutyric acid) được tăng\r\nđáng kể.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:6.0pt; margin-left:0in;text-align:justify;line-height:12.0pt&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;- Công dụng của&amp;nbsp;Gạo Mầm Vibigaba&amp;nbsp;là:&lt;/span&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;