l&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Dạng lỏng:\r\nHấp thu nhanh, đến khớp với nồng độ cao, dễ dung nạp, được ưa chuộng.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;5. Dùng trong bao lâu?\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Dùng điều\r\ntrị cho đến khi hết các triệu chứng khớp.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Dùng lâu\r\ndài để bồi bổ sụn khớp và ngăn tái phát.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://http/tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;6. Tác dụng phụ của thuốc là gì?\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p 