  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Pha với\r\nnhiều nước hơn (1,5 - 2L)\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Ngưng\r\nthuốc kháng viêm\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Hoặc pha\r\nloãng ít và uống ngay trước hoặc trong bữa ăn.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;\r\nGlucosamine không có hại cho dạ dày. ngược lại còn giúp tạo chất nhờn che chở\r\ndạ dày và tạo collagen giúp vết loét dạ dày mau lành.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://http/tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&quot;&gt;http://tranglypharma.com/xuong-khop/traly-samin&lt;/a&gt;\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;8. Người dị ứng với hải sản có dùng được Glucosamine không?\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Vẫn dùng\r\nđược trên thực tế.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Mặc dù về\r\nlý thuyết nhà sản xuất cẩn thận lưu ý.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp; Nguyên\r\nnhân gây dị ứng là thịt hải sản, không nằm trong vỏ hải sản.\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif; font-weight: bold;&quot;&gt;9. Loại Glucosamine nào tốt nhất?\r\n    &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;, serif;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;\r\nGlucosamine hydrochloride.\r\n   &lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0.0001pt;&quot;&gt;\r\n  &lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 13.5pt; font-family: &#039;Times New Roman